name: Enter The Wu-Tang Action Figure
description:
Digital custom action figure representation of Wu-Tang’s debut, one of the greatest album ever released in hip hop (and probably any other existing music) history. Seriously if you’ve never heard of -at leat- “Protect Ya Neck”, then WHAT THE HELL HAVE YOU BEEN DOING with your life??!!!

Card is made from Enter The Wu-Tang 36 Chambers cover shot, how could you NOT know that???

Figure is made from MOTU Classics He-Man figure, Super 7’s Killa Mike & ODB figure, NECA’s Michael Myers figure and a customized MF DOOM figure.
